What’s New¶

  • 15.5.0.0

    • New Microsoft Project interface

      A new interface between CONTACT’s project management and Microsoft Project has been developed, mainly based on the XML format of Microsoft Project. From now on the old Microsoft Project interface shipped until cs.officelink 15.3 is no longer supported. For further information please see the manuals of Projects and OfficeLink.

    • Server-side and thus customizable evaluation of document variables via the modes rs, ws and rws.
